1080
01:23:47,896 --> 01:23:49,574
I'm afraid he's changed his mind.

1081
01:23:50,164 --> 01:23:52,501
The doctor started to
believe his own propaganda.

1082
01:23:52,761 --> 01:23:54,295
I mean you dream this guy, Edward.

1083
01:23:54,296 --> 01:23:55,296
Help, get him elected.

1084
01:23:55,297 --> 01:23:56,577
Those are the Soviets

1085
01:23:56,612 --> 01:23:58,921
International Department
