1093
01:24:22,328 --> 01:24:23,328
Can you go back.

1094
01:24:23,996 --> 01:24:25,675
Go. Go back a little bit.

1095
01:24:29,233 --> 01:24:30,384
Run it from there.

1096
01:24:45,705 --> 01:24:47,251
I just thought I saw something.

1097
01:24:47,695 --> 01:24:50,008
I want you two to put your
