01:24:55,816 --> 01:24:56,557
non official

1102
01:24:57,759 --> 01:24:59,189
He'll be our eyes and ears.

1103
01:25:00,222 --> 01:25:00,908
Congratulations.

1104
01:25:00,947 --> 01:25:01,375
