1105
01:25:02,606 --> 01:25:03,216
Good luck.

1106
01:25:03,380 --> 01:25:04,098
Thank you.

1107
01:25:04,904 --> 01:25:06,375
I wouldn't wear my
class ring down there.

1108
01:25:07,244 --> 01:25:08,424
Yes sir. Of course.

1109
01:25:08,425 --> 01:25:10,317
I want all intelligence on this

